abstract: Thursday’s season finale of “Project Runway” on Bravo drew an average of 3.75 million viewers in the 18- to 49-year-old demographic, topping two of the three broadcast networks (ABC and CBS) at 10 p.m.
lead_paragraph: Thursday’s season finale of “Project Runway” on Bravo drew an average of 3.75 million viewers in the 18- to 49-year-old demographic, topping two of the three broadcast networks (ABC and CBS) at 10 p.m.

headline.main: ‘Runway’ Finale Breaks Ratings Record for Bravo
